ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Gros Cap Indian Reserve No. 49, in Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 1,336.633 hectares (3,302.892 acres) of lands, including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Michipicoten First Nation as an addition to GROS CAP INDIAN RESERVE NO.49, located in the municipal Township of Wawa and is approximately 233 kilometres from Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario.
